						               													<description>Game description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Discovering the tradition of the 19th-century Mazovia region via a card game? Why not! Ryzykanci: Koleje Fortuny (Daredevils: Wheels of Fortune) presents the time of revolutionary industrial changes, political storms, building fortunes, and the first steps of the capitalistic society in Poland. The rail played an important role at that time; it revolutionized transportation, production and trade. Welcome to Mazovia, the world of industrialists, tycoons, magnates and patrons &amp;ndash; in other words, daredevils.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game you take a role of a famous Polish industrailist from the 19th century and develop your company. The goal of the game is to achieve the highest number of prestige points. Players may gather prestige points through buying shares, building investments (such as Train Stations, Theaters or Boarding Schools) and collecting cash.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The box contains: 110 cards, 16 wood markers and a rulebook with an educational brochure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game was prepared for the Mazovian Center of Culture and Art.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
